<note type="date" xml:id="date">
    <p>This small sheet probably dates from September or October 1875, in a period when the subject of bread came up several times. In <ref target="let052.xml">letter 52</ref> of 29 September that year, Vincent asks Theo if he has started eating extra bread yet, and he speaks of it again in <ref target="let055.xml">letters 55</ref> and <ref target="let056.xml">56</ref> of October. In <hi rend="ital">De brieven</hi> 1990 this note was printed with letter 49 of Friday, 17 September 1875, but we can see no good reason for that.</p>
                    </note>
